(117, 'Sunshine 250W Mono Solar Panel', 'Monocrystaline', 115, 70000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6995cba2e2bea4.59765173.jpeg', 'Sunshine 250W Mono Solar Panel\r\n\r\nPower your home or business with reliable, high-efficiency solar energy using the Sunshine 250W / 24V Monocrystalline Solar Panel. Built with premium mono solar cells, this panel delivers strong performance, even in low-light conditions, making it ideal for Nigeria’s climate and year-round sunlight exposure.\r\n\r\nDesigned for durability and long-term output stability, the Sunshine 250W panel is perfect for residential systems, commercial installations, off-grid setups, solar street lighting, and backup power solutions.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re setting up a new solar system or expanding an existing one, this 24V panel offers dependable energy generation and excellent value for money.\r\n\r\n\r\nIdeal For:\r\n\r\n* Homes & residential solar systems\r\n* Offices & commercial buildings\r\n* Solar inverter systems\r\n* Off-grid installations\r\n* Telecom sites\r\n* Farms & rural electrification projects\r\n\r\n\r\nWhy Choose Sunshine 250W / 24V Mono Solar Panel?\r\n\r\n✔ Reliable power output\r\n✔ Built for harsh weather conditions\r\n✔ Long service life\r\n✔ Cost-effective energy solution\r\n✔ Trusted performance for 24V systems\r\n\r\nMake the smart switch to clean, renewable energy today with the Sunshine 250W / 24V Monocrystalline Solar Panel — dependable power you can trust.\r\n\r\n', '2026-02-28 16:08:04', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6995cc0e38c876.21408151.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other ', '250w, solar, panels, mono, sunlight ', '[{\"title\":\"250 Watts Rated Power Output\",\"detail\":\"Efficient and consistent energy production\"},{\"title\":\"Monocrystalline Solar Cells\",\"detail\":\"Higher efficiency and better performance in limited sunlight\"},{\"title\":\"High Conversion Efficiency\",\"detail\":\"Maximizes power generation per square meter\"},{\"title\":\"Strong Aluminum Frame\",\"detail\":\"Corrosion-resistant and weatherproof\"},{\"title\":\"Tempered Glass Surface\",\"detail\":\"Durable, impact-resistant protection\"},{\"title\":\"Low Degradation Rate\",\"detail\":\"Long lifespan with stable performance\"}]', NULL),
(118, 'Sunshine 600W Mono Solar Panel', 'Monocrystaline', 115, 135000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6995e4824058e5.41007076.jpeg', 'Sunshine 600W Mono Solar Panel\r\n\r\nPower your home or business with reliable, high-efficiency solar energy using the Sunshine 600W Monocrystalline Solar Panel. Built with premium mono solar cells, this panel delivers strong performance, even in low-light conditions, making it ideal for Nigeria’s climate and year-round sunlight exposure.\r\n\r\nDesigned for durability and long-term output stability, the Sunshine 600W panel is perfect for residential systems, commercial installations, off-grid setups, solar street lighting, and backup power solutions.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re setting up a new solar system or expanding an existing one, this 24V panel offers dependable energy generation and excellent value for money.\r\n\r\n\r\nWhy Choose Sunshine 600W / 24V Mono Solar Panel?\r\n\r\n✔ Reliable power output\r\n✔ Built for harsh weather conditions\r\n✔ Long service life\r\n✔ Cost-effective energy solution\r\n✔ Trusted performance for 24V systems\r\n\r\nMake the smart switch to clean, renewable energy today with the Sunshine 600W / 24V Monocrystalline Solar Panel — dependable power you can trust.\r\n', '2026-02-28 16:07:43', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6995e5d981a2b2.96806047.png', NULL, 0, 'Other', '600w,  mono, solar, panel, string aluminum ', '[{\"title\":\"600 Watts Rated Power Output\",\"detail\":\"Efficient and consistent energy production\"},{\"title\":\"Monocrystalline Solar Cells\",\"detail\":\"Higher efficiency and better performance in limited sunlight\"},{\"title\":\"High Conversion Efficiency\",\"detail\":\"High Conversion Efficiency\"},{\"title\":\"Strong Aluminum Frame\",\"detail\":\"Corrosion-resistant and weatherproof\"},{\"title\":\"Tempered Glass Surface\",\"detail\":\"Durable, impact-resistant protection\"},{\"title\":\"Low Degradation Rate\",\"detail\":\"Long lifespan with stable performance\"},{\"title\":\"Easy Installation\",\"detail\":\"Compatible with standard mounting systems\"}]', NULL),
(119, '550W Monocrystalline Solar Panel', 'Monocrystaline', 115, 125000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6995eb83b4ca95.79957688.jpeg', '550W Monocrystalline Solar Panel \r\n\r\nPower large loads with fewer panels. The 550W Monocrystalline Solar Panel is a high-efficiency module designed for serious residential and commercial solar systems. Built with advanced mono-crystalline cells, it captures more sunlight and converts it into usable energy even in cloudy or low-light conditions — making it perfect for Nigeria and other high-temperature regions.\r\n\r\nIts durable tempered glass surface, corrosion-resistant aluminum frame, and waterproof junction box ensure long-term outdoor performance in rain, heat, and dust. With higher wattage output, you install fewer panels while getting more power — reducing mounting space, wiring cost, and installation time.\r\n\r\nIdeal for powering:\r\n\r\n* Homes & apartments\r\n* Shops & offices\r\n* Inverter & battery backup systems\r\n* Solar street lights\r\n* Boreholes & water pumps\r\n* CCTV & security systems\r\n* Farms and rural electrification\r\n\r\nWhether you’re upgrading an existing setup or building a full solar solution, this panel delivers reliable, stable energy every day.\r\n\r\n\r\nKey Highlights:\r\n\r\n* 550W high output power\r\n* 24V system compatible\r\n* Monocrystalline high efficiency cells\r\n* Performs well in hot weather\r\n* Strong aluminum frame + tempered glass\r\n* Long lifespan (20+ years typical performance life)\r\n* Lower installation cost per watt\r\n\r\nReliable power. Bigger output. Fewer panels.\r\n', '2026-02-28 16:07:04', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6995eb83b4e114.35198288.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '550w, mono crystalline, high power, solar, panel', '[{\"title\":\"550W High Power Output\",\"detail\":\"Generate more electricity with fewer panels, saving roof space and installation cost.\"},{\"title\":\"Monocrystalline Solar Cells\",\"detail\":\"Higher efficiency and better performance even in low sunlight conditions.\"},{\"title\":\"High Conversion Efficiency\",\"detail\":\"More sunlight converted into usable power, increasing daily energy production.\"},{\"title\":\"Tempered Glass Surface\",\"detail\":\"Strong protection against impact, rain, and harsh weather.\"},{\"title\":\"Corrosion-Resistant Aluminum Frame\",\"detail\":\"Long-lasting durability, especially in humid or coastal areas.\"},{\"title\":\"Weatherproof Junction Box (IP Rated)\",\"detail\":\"Safe and reliable performance during heavy rain and dust exposure.\"},{\"title\":\"Low Degradation Rate\",\"detail\":\"Maintains performance for 20+ years with minimal power loss.\"}]', NULL),
(120, '5Kwh SMS Lithium Battery', 'Lithium Battery', 34, 1200000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6996e0598b5532.95784295.jpeg', '5KWh SMS Lithium Battery \r\n\r\nUpgrade your solar power system with the 5KWh SMS Lithium Battery, a modern energy storage solution designed for reliable, long-lasting backup power. Built with advanced lithium (LiFePO₄) technology, this battery stores excess solar energy during the day and delivers clean, stable electricity whenever you need it — day or night.\r\n\r\nUnlike traditional lead-acid batteries, the SMS lithium battery charges faster, lasts significantly longer, and requires zero maintenance. Its intelligent Battery Management System (BMS) protects against over-charging, deep discharge, overheating, and short circuits, ensuring safety and consistent performance for homes, offices, shops, and hybrid solar installations.\r\n\r\nCompact wall-mount design, smart display monitoring, and high efficiency make it perfect for inverter systems, reducing generator usage and cutting electricity costs.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re dealing with unstable grid power or want full energy independence, the 5KWh SMS Lithium Battery keeps your lights, appliances, and essential electronics running smoothly.', '2026-02-28 14:07:40', 'uploads/image_1_6996e0598b6a58.50671105.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_6996e0598b8063.79280112.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'SMS', '5kwh, sms, lithium, battery, energy, fast charging ', '[{\"title\":\"5KWh Energy Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Powers essential home and office appliances for long backup hours\"},{\"title\":\"LiFePO\\u2084 Lithium Technology\",\"detail\":\"4\\u20136\\u00d7 longer lifespan than lead-acid batteries\"},{\"title\":\"Built-in Smart BMS Protection\",\"detail\":\"Prevents damage, overheating, and battery failure\"},{\"title\":\"Fast Charging Capability\",\"detail\":\"Stores solar energy quickly even with limited sunlight\"},{\"title\":\"Deep Discharge Support (80\\u201395% DoD)\",\"detail\":\"More usable power from every charge\"},{\"title\":\"Maintenance-Free Operation\",\"detail\":\"No water topping, no acid leaks, no stress\"},{\"title\":\"Wall-Mount Compact Design\",\"detail\":\"Saves space and keeps installation neat\"},{\"title\":\"LCD Monitoring Display\",\"detail\":\"Easily check battery level, voltage & performance\"},{\"title\":\"High Efficiency Output\",\"detail\":\"Stable power for TVs, fridges, routers & electronics\"},{\"title\":\"Solar & Inverter Compatible\",\"detail\":\"Works perfectly with hybrid and off-grid systems\"}]', NULL),
(121, '5Kwh Taico Lithium Battery', 'Lithium Battery', 34, 1050000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6996e668179802.17098947.jpeg', '5KWh Taico Lithium Battery\r\n\r\nPower your home or business with dependable, long-lasting energy storage.\r\n\r\nThe 5KWh Taico Lithium Battery is a high-performance solar storage solution designed to store excess solar energy during the day and supply stable electricity whenever you need it — day or night.\r\n\r\nBuilt with advanced LiFePO₄ (Lithium Iron Phosphate) technology, this battery delivers superior safety, longer lifespan, faster charging, and deeper discharge compared to traditional lead-acid batteries. It’s the perfect upgrade for solar systems, inverters, and backup power setups where reliability matters.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re dealing with frequent outages or aiming for energy independence, the Taico 5KWh battery ensures uninterrupted power for lighting, TVs, routers, offices, and essential appliances.\r\n\r\nIdeal for homes, shops, offices, schools, and off-grid installations.', '2026-02-28 14:07:17', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6996e66817abd8.16492021.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Tiaco', '5KWh, Taico, Lithium Battery, power, fast charging', '[{\"title\":\"5KWh Energy Storage Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Powers essential appliances for longer hours without grid electricity\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO\\u2084) Cells\",\"detail\":\"Much safer, no overheating, no explosion risk\"},{\"title\":\"6000+ Charge Cycles\",\"detail\":\"Lasts 8\\u201315 years \\u2014 far longer than lead-acid batteries\"},{\"title\":\"Deep Discharge Capability (90\\u2013100% DoD)\",\"detail\":\"You can use almost all the stored power without damaging the battery\"},{\"title\":\"Fast Charging Support\",\"detail\":\"Recharges quickly during sunlight hours\"},{\"title\":\"Built-in Battery Management System (BMS)\",\"detail\":\"Automatic protection against overcharge, short circuit & overheating\"},{\"title\":\"Stable Output Voltage\",\"detail\":\"Protects sensitive electronics and inverter components\"},{\"title\":\"Wall-mount \\/ Compact Design\",\"detail\":\"Saves space and keeps installation neat\"},{\"title\":\"Maintenance-Free Operation\",\"detail\":\"No water topping, no acid leaks, no stress\"},{\"title\":\"Compatible with Most Inverters\",\"detail\":\"Works easily with hybrid and solar inverter systems\"}]', NULL),
(122, 'Felicity 12V 200Ah Gel Pattern Battery', 'Gel Pattern battery', 74, 260000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6996ea414634c0.37782566.jpeg', 'Felicity 12V 200Ah Gel Pattern Battery \r\n\r\nPower your home, office, or solar system with a battery built for reliability and long backup hours. The 12V 200Ah Gel Pattern Battery is a deep-cycle energy storage battery designed specifically for solar inverters, UPS systems, and backup power applications where steady performance matters.\r\n\r\nUnlike ordinary car batteries, this gel battery uses advanced gel electrolyte technology that prevents leakage, reduces maintenance, and allows deeper discharge without damaging the battery. That means longer lifespan, safer indoor installation, and consistent power during outages.\r\n\r\nPerfect for homes facing frequent power cuts, shops, CCTV systems, and solar installations — it delivers dependable electricity day after day while requiring almost zero maintenance.\r\n\r\nIts sealed, vibration-resistant design makes it ideal for both indoor and outdoor energy storage setups.', '2026-02-28 14:13:42', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6996ea41464bc0.43664819.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other ', 'Gel, battery, 200Ah, Felicity, long cycle', '[{\"title\":\"Gel electrolyte technology\",\"detail\":\"No acid spills, safer indoor installation\"},{\"title\":\"200Ah high capacity\",\"detail\":\"Longer backup during power outages\"},{\"title\":\"Deep-cycle design\",\"detail\":\"Can discharge daily without quick damage\"},{\"title\":\"Maintenance-free\",\"detail\":\"No topping up water or regular servicing\"},{\"title\":\"Low self-discharge\",\"detail\":\"Holds charge for long periods when unused\"},{\"title\":\"Heat resistant build\",\"detail\":\"Performs well in hot environments\"},{\"title\":\"Sealed battery casing\",\"detail\":\"Clean installation in homes & offices\"},{\"title\":\"Long cycle life\",\"detail\":\"Saves money by reducing replacement frequency\"}]', NULL),
(123, '12V 100AH Gel Sunfit battery', 'Gel Pattern battery', 74, 122000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6996ef88d18763.03746416.jpeg', '12V 100AH Gel Sunfit Battery \r\n\r\nPower your home, office, or solar system with dependable long-lasting energy. The Sunfit 12V 100AH Gel Battery is a deep-cycle maintenance-free battery engineered for solar backup, inverters, and off-grid power systems where reliability matters every single day.\r\n\r\nUnlike regular car batteries, this gel battery is built to discharge slowly and recharge repeatedly without damage — making it perfect for frequent power outages and daily solar usage.\r\n\r\nIts sealed gel electrolyte technology prevents acid leakage, reduces maintenance, and significantly increases lifespan compared to traditional flooded batteries.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re running lights, fans, TVs, routers, or small appliances, the Sunfit battery delivers stable voltage, protects your inverter, and keeps your home powered quietly and safely.', '2026-02-28 14:16:00', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6996ef88d19e49.84002883.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '12v, sms, gel, 100h, battery, sunfit', '[{\"title\":\"12V 100AH Gel Sunfit Battery \\u2014 Product Description Power your home, office, or solar system with dependable long-lasting energy. The Sunfit 12V 100AH Gel Battery is a deep-cycle maintenance-free battery engineered for solar backup, inverters, and off-grid power systems where reliability matters every single day. Unlike regular car batteries, this gel battery is built to discharge slowly and recharge repeatedly without damage \\u2014 making it perfect for frequent power outages and daily solar usage. Its sealed gel electrolyte technology prevents acid leakage, reduces maintenance, and significantly increases lifespan compared to traditional flooded batteries. Whether you\'re running lights, fans, TVs, routers, or small appliances, the Sunfit battery delivers stable voltage, protects your inverter, and keeps your home powered quietly and safely.\",\"detail\":\"Designed for long backup hours\"},{\"title\":\"Gel Technology\",\"detail\":\"Spill-proof & maintenance-free\"},{\"title\":\"Long Service Life\",\"detail\":\"More charge cycles than regular batteries\"},{\"title\":\"Low Self-Discharge\",\"detail\":\"Holds power for longer periods\"},{\"title\":\"Fast Recharge Efficiency\",\"detail\":\"Ideal for solar panels & inverters\"},{\"title\":\"Stable Voltage Output\",\"detail\":\"Protects appliances from fluctuations\"}]', NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `category`, `category_id`, `price`, `image_main`, `description`, `created_at`, `image_1`, `image_2`, `image_3`, `is_featured`, `brand`, `tags`, `specifications`, `sub_category_id`) VALUES
(124, 'Felicity 5kwh 51v lithium battery', 'Lithium Battery', 34, 480000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6996f49f6b83a6.17214340.jpeg', '5kWh 51V Lithium Battery \r\n\r\nPower outages shouldn’t interrupt your life or business. The 5kWh 51V Lithium Battery is a modern energy storage solution designed to store solar power efficiently and deliver stable electricity whenever you need it — day or night.\r\n\r\nBuilt with advanced LiFePO₄ lithium technology, this battery offers longer lifespan, faster charging, deeper discharge capacity, and superior safety compared to traditional lead-acid batteries. It’s perfect for solar systems, inverters, offices, shops, and residential backup power.\r\n\r\nWhether you want to reduce generator use, cut fuel costs, or enjoy silent uninterrupted electricity, this battery provides dependable performance for years.', '2026-02-28 14:08:07', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_6996f49f6b95e2.42476941.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Felicity ', '5kwh, lithium, battery, 51v, deep cycle, long life span, solar, inverter', '[{\"title\":\"capacity\",\"detail\":\"5kwh\"},{\"title\":\"Nominal Voltage\",\"detail\":\"51.2v\"},{\"title\":\"Battery Type\",\"detail\":\"Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO\\u2084)\"},{\"title\":\"Deep Cycle Performance\",\"detail\":\"Up to 90\\u2013100% usable capacity\"},{\"title\":\"Long Life Span\",\"detail\":\"4000\\u20136000+ cycles\"},{\"title\":\"Built-in BMS Protection\",\"detail\":\"Over-charge, over-discharge, short circuit & temperature\"}]', NULL),
(125, 'Colar 1000 Solar Generator', 'Solar Generator', 77, 300000.00, 'uploads/image_main_69983590bb1813.08511701.png', 'Meet the Colar 1000 Solar Generator! This powerful device provides backup power for your essentials like TVs, rechargeable fan, laptops, bulbs, and phones. It comes with:\r\n\r\n- A 1000Wh lithium battery\r\n- Solar, grid(NEPA)/ generator charging options\r\n- Can be connected with up to 200watts solar panel to charge through solar with the inbuilt controller\r\n- Automatic switching between grid and battery power, Stay powered up seamlessly, even during outages!\r\n\r\nInverter Capacity - 200W\r\nBattery Capacity -1kwh\r\nBattery Type - Lithium\r\n', '2026-02-20 10:21:04', 'uploads/image_1_69983590bb9831.15923945.jpg', '', '', 0, 'ColaSolar', 'solar,solar generator,energy', '[]', NULL),
(127, 'Colar 1000pro Solar Generator', 'Solar Generator', 77, 340000.00, 'uploads/image_main_69983d7ac08e95.92913250.png', 'The ColaSolar 1000 Pro is a portable solar power station, a compact home energy storage system with a 1000Wh (1kWh) lithium battery, designed for backup power with features like pure sine wave AC output (around 300W), automatic grid switching, and compatibility with solar panels (up to 200W) for powering essentials like lights, phones, TVs, and laptops during outages, making it suitable for home, camping, or off-grid use.\r\n\r\nThe box contains:\r\n1 x 1000 solar power Generator \r\n\r\n1 x MC4 connector \r\n\r\n1 x grid adaptor \r\n\r\nUser manual ', '2026-02-20 10:54:50', 'uploads/image_1_69983d7ac11d68.65088630.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 'ColaSolar', '', '[{\"title\":\"Product Specifications\",\"detail\":\"Model: colar 1000W PRO Rated power :300W Rated Capacity:1KWH(314ah) Ac Output Voltage  220v Ac input Voltage  220V Ac input Frequency 45-65Hz Ac Output Frequency  50-60Hz Ac Input power 350W PV input Voltage  12-60V Maximum Pv input power :200W BATTERY type  :LifeP04 Operating Temperature Range :0-45C Operating Humidity Range  90% Max Operating  Altitude  <3000m\"}]', NULL),
(131, 'Colar 2000 Solar Generator', 'Solar Generator', 77, 640000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699840ec537059.16120778.png', 'ColaSolar 2000W Solar Generator\r\nEquipped with two 314Ah lithium batteries, the system offers a total capacity of 2000Wh. It features an 800W AC input, 450W DC input, and delivers a stable 1000W 220V AC output. Designed for versatility, it’s ideal for powering homes, offices, workstation etc.\r\n\r\nIdeal For:\r\n\r\nPower backup during blackouts\r\nSolar energy storage\r\nReducing generator usage\r\nDaily home or small office energy needs\r\nInvest in reliable power today with the Cola 2KWH Lithium Battery System – your smart backup energy solution.', '2026-02-20 11:09:32', 'uploads/image_1_699840ec540326.85041028.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 'ColaSolar', 'solar,solar generator,energy', '[]', NULL),
(132, 'Colar 3600', 'Solar Generator', 77, 820000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6998423e5fb264.32972723.png', 'Stay powered anytime, anywhere with the Cola Solar 3.6kWh Solar Generator. Built with advanced Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO₄) battery technology, this solar generator delivers long-lasting, safe, and eco-friendly power for both home and outdoor use. With a capacity of 3600Wh and a 1200W pure sine wave inverter, it can efficiently run essential appliances like TVs, laptops, fans, fridges, projectors, hairdryers, ventilators, and more.\r\n\r\n ', '2026-02-20 11:15:10', 'uploads/image_1_6998423e603f32.69334670.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 'ColaSolar', 'solar,solar generator,energy', '[{\"title\":\"Product Specifications\",\"detail\":\"SKU: BR094GP7WLC0JNAFAMZ Weight (kg): 32 Color: WHITE ORANGE AND GREEN\"}]', NULL),
(133, 'Colar 3600pro', 'Solar Generator', 77, 1020000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699842fab30e24.38367274.png', 'Stay powered anytime, anywhere with the Cola Solar 3.6kWh Solar Generator. Built with advanced Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO₄) battery technology, this solar generator delivers long-lasting, safe, and eco-friendly power for both home and outdoor use. With a capacity of 3600Wh and a 1200W pure sine wave inverter, it can efficiently run essential appliances like TVs, laptops, fans, fridges, projectors, hairdryers, ventilators, and more.', '2026-02-20 11:18:18', 'uploads/image_1_699842fab3c225.75723349.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 'ColaSolar', 'solar,solar generator,energy', '[]', NULL),
(134, 'Dura Volt DC Standing Fan (16”)', 'Standing Fan 1', 112, 45000.00, 'uploads/image_main_69984f5c4bda79.03978806.jpeg', 'Dura Volt DC Standing Fan (16”)\r\n\r\nStay cool even during power outages with the Dura Volt 16-inch DC Standing Fan — a smart energy-saving cooling solution designed for homes and offices using inverter or solar power systems. \r\nBuilt with a high-efficiency DC motor, this fan delivers strong airflow while consuming far less electricity than conventional AC fans.\r\n\r\nPerfect for areas with unstable electricity, the Dura Volt DC fan keeps running smoothly on batteries, inverters, or solar setups — giving you comfort without draining your power storage.\r\n\r\nIts adjustable height, wide oscillation, and quiet operation make it ideal for bedrooms, living rooms, shops, and workplaces where silence and efficiency matter.', '2026-02-28 15:42:28', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Dura Volt', 'Dura volt, DC, fan, 16-inch', '[{\"title\":\"DC Motor Technology\",\"detail\":\"Runs longer on battery & inverter power\"},{\"title\":\"Low Energy Consumption\",\"detail\":\"Saves electricity bills daily\"},{\"title\":\"16\\u201d Blade Size\",\"detail\":\"Strong airflow cools the room faster\"},{\"title\":\"Quiet Operation\",\"detail\":\"Sleep and work without noise disturbance\"},{\"title\":\"Adjustable Height & Tilt\",\"detail\":\"Direct airflow exactly where needed\"},{\"title\":\"Solar Compatible\",\"detail\":\"Works perfectly with solar systems\"},{\"title\":\"Strong Tripod Base\",\"detail\":\"Stable and safe placement anywhere\"}]', NULL),
(135, 'Dura Volt DC Standing Fan (18”)', 'Standing Fan 1', 112, 50000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6998524a702192.92375348.jpeg', 'Dura Volt DC Standing Fan (18”)\r\n\r\nStay cool even during power outages with the Dura Volt 18-inch DC Standing Fan — a smart energy-saving cooling solution designed for homes and offices using inverter or solar power systems. Built with a high-efficiency DC motor, this fan delivers strong airflow while consuming far less electricity than conventional AC fans.\r\n\r\nPerfect for areas with unstable electricity, the Dura Volt DC fan keeps running smoothly on batteries, inverters, or solar setups — giving you comfort without draining your power storage.\r\n\r\nIts adjustable height, wide oscillation, and quiet operation make it ideal for bedrooms, living rooms, shops, and workplaces where silence and efficiency matter.', '2026-02-28 15:43:43', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Dura Volt', 'Ultra low power, 18-inch, DC, fan, dura volt, standing fan', '[{\"title\":\"18\\u201d Blade Size\",\"detail\":\"Strong airflow cools the room faster\"},{\"title\":\"Quiet Operation\",\"detail\":\"Sleep and work without noise disturbance\"},{\"title\":\"Strong Tripod Base\",\"detail\":\"Stable and safe placement anywhere\"},{\"title\":\"Solar Compatible\",\"detail\":\"Works perfectly with solar systems\"},{\"title\":\"Low Energy Consumption\",\"detail\":\"Saves electricity bills daily\"},{\"title\":\"Oscillation Function\",\"detail\":\"Even air distribution across the room\"}]', NULL),
(136, 'Dura Volt DC Wall Fan \"16', 'Wall Fan1', 114, 45000.00, 'uploads/image_main_6998554e4879e5.93880612.jpeg', 'Dura Volt DC Wall Fan 16\"\r\n\r\nStay cool even during power outages with the Dura Volt 16-Inch DC Wall Fan — a low-energy cooling solution specially designed for solar and inverter systems. Built with an efficient DC motor, this fan consumes far less electricity than conventional AC fans, making it perfect for homes, shops, offices, and off-grid environments.\r\n\r\nIts wall-mounted design saves space while delivering strong airflow across the room. The quiet motor ensures comfortable cooling without disturbing sleep, work, or relaxation. Whether connected to a solar panel, battery, or inverter, the Dura Volt DC fan keeps running when grid power fails.\r\n\r\nReliable, economical, and energy-smart — this is the cooling solution made for modern energy-saving homes.', '2026-02-28 15:50:01', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Dura Volt', 'Dura Volt, DC, wall fan, 16-inch', '[{\"title\":\"Quiet operation\",\"detail\":\"Sleep and work without noise disturbance\"},{\"title\":\"16-inch wide blade\",\"detail\":\"For powerful air circulation\"},{\"title\":\"Heat-resistant copper coil motor\",\"detail\":\"For long lifespan\"},{\"title\":\"Low Energy Consumption\",\"detail\":\"Saves electricity bills daily\"}]', NULL),
(137, 'Battery Equalizer (48V)', '48v', 84, 78000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699c3491a9df09.32876293.jpeg', 'Battery Equalizer (48V) – Product Description\r\n\r\nProtect your battery investment and extend its lifespan with the 48V Battery Equalizer — a smart voltage balancing device designed for battery banks connected in series.\r\n\r\nWhen multiple batteries are connected together (especially in 48V systems), slight voltage differences naturally occur over time. These imbalances can reduce battery performance, shorten lifespan, and lead to premature battery failure. \r\nThe 48V Battery Equalizer automatically balances voltage across each battery, ensuring they charge and discharge evenly.', '2026-02-23 11:05:53', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699c3491a9fc97.99812370.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '48v, battery , equalizer, ', '[{\"title\":\"Designed for 48V battery systems\",\"detail\":\"Perfectly suited for solar, inverter, and industrial 48V setups\"},{\"title\":\"Automatic voltage balancing\",\"detail\":\"Prevents uneven charging that damages batteries\"},{\"title\":\"Energy transfer between batteries\",\"detail\":\"Keeps all batteries at equal voltage for maximum efficiency\"},{\"title\":\"Compatible with Lead-Acid, AGM, GEL & LiFePO\\u2084\",\"detail\":\"Works with most common battery types\"},{\"title\":\"Prevents overcharging & undercharging\",\"detail\":\"Protects individual batteries from early failure\"},{\"title\":\"Improves overall battery performance\",\"detail\":\"Longer backup time and better system stability\"},{\"title\":\"Extends battery lifespan\",\"detail\":\"Saves money by reducing battery replacement costs\"},{\"title\":\"Compact & durable design\",\"detail\":\"Easy to install and built for long-term use\"}]', NULL),
(138, 'Battery Equalizer (24V)', '24v', 85, 34000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699c3aed482903.68961960.jpeg', 'Battery Equalizer (24V)\r\n\r\nKeep your 24V battery system balanced, efficient, and long-lasting with the Battery Equalizer (24V) — a smart voltage balancing device designed to protect batteries connected in series.\r\n\r\nWhen two 12V batteries are connected to form a 24V system, voltage differences naturally develop over time. These imbalances can cause one battery to overcharge while the other undercharges — reducing performance and shortening battery life.\r\n\r\nThe 24V Battery Equalizer automatically monitors and balances the voltage between batteries, ensuring they charge and discharge evenly for maximum efficiency and reliability.', '2026-02-23 11:38:08', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699c3aed483f83.98904599.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other ', '24v, battery, equalizer ', '[{\"title\":\"Designed for 24V battery systems\",\"detail\":\"Perfectly balances two 12V batteries connected in series\"},{\"title\":\"Automatic voltage balancing\",\"detail\":\"Prevents one battery from overcharging or undercharging\"},{\"title\":\"Real-time voltage monitoring\",\"detail\":\"Ensures continuous protection without manual checks\"},{\"title\":\"Energy transfer between batteries\",\"detail\":\"Keeps both batteries at equal charge levels\"},{\"title\":\"Compatible with Lead-Acid, AGM, GEL & LiFePO\\u2084\",\"detail\":\"Works with most common solar and inverter batteries\"},{\"title\":\"Prevents battery imbalance damage\",\"detail\":\"Reduces risk of premature battery failure\"},{\"title\":\"Improves charging efficiency\",\"detail\":\"Maximizes system performance and backup time\"},{\"title\":\"Extends battery lifespan\",\"detail\":\"Saves money on frequent battery replacements\"},{\"title\":\"Low power consumption\",\"detail\":\"Operates efficiently without draining your system\"}]', NULL),
(139, 'Qasa Solar Ceiling Fan', 'Ceiling Fan1', 113, 55000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699c47c5675848.33101310.jpeg', 'Qasa Solar Ceiling Fan (AC/DC)\r\n\r\nStay cool — even when there’s no electricity.\r\n\r\nThe Qasa Solar Ceiling Fan is a high-efficiency AC/DC ceiling fan designed to work with solar panels, batteries, and regular electricity (NEPA). It gives you reliable cooling during power outages while helping you reduce electricity costs.\r\n\r\nBuilt for homes, offices, shops, and off-grid locations, this fan combines energy efficiency, quiet performance, and flexible power options — making it perfect for Nigerian weather and unstable power supply.', '2026-02-28 15:47:04', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699c47c5677621.51138540.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Qasa', 'Fan, low power, solar, quiet, powerful, ceiling fan', '[{\"title\":\"Dual Power Advantage (AC\\/DC)\",\"detail\":\"Works with PHCN\\/NEPA electricity (AC) and Works with solar panels and batteries (DC)\"},{\"title\":\"Solar-Ready & Energy Efficient\",\"detail\":\"Designed to consume low power, this fan runs efficiently on solar systems without draining your batteries quickly.\"},{\"title\":\"Quiet & Powerful Performance\",\"detail\":\"Strong airflow. Quiet operation\"},{\"title\":\"Durable & Built for Nigerian Conditions\",\"detail\":\"Long-lasting internal components and designed for hot climates\"}]', NULL),
(140, '300w Qasa low power dry iron', 'Dry iron', 94, 34000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699c4c6ceb33e3.89943070.png', '300W Qasa Low Power Dry Iron – Reliable, Efficient, Everyday Ironing\r\n\r\nThe 300W Qasa Low Power Dry Iron delivers dependable performance with energy-saving efficiency — making it the perfect choice for everyday ironing tasks. Engineered with simplicity and durability in mind, this dry iron is ideal for homes, hostels, guest houses, and small businesses that need a practical, no-nonsense iron that gets the job done without consuming excess power.', '2026-02-28 16:32:52', 'uploads/image_1_699c4cf42c8f97.83053366.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_699c4cf42ca7a0.33437907.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Qasa', '300w, Qasa, Low power, dry iron ', '[{\"title\":\"Powerful 300W Heating\",\"detail\":\"Quick and consistent heat distribution for smooth, effective ironing without waiting.\"},{\"title\":\"Low Power Consumption\",\"detail\":\"Energy-efficient design helps reduce electricity costs while delivering excellent ironing performance.\"},{\"title\":\"Ergonomic Comfort Grip\",\"detail\":\"Lightweight and easy to handle \\u2014 reduces hand fatigue during prolonged use.\"},{\"title\":\"Durable Soleplate\",\"detail\":\"Smooth, non-stick soleplate glides easily over fabrics for crease-free results every time.\"},{\"title\":\"Simple Temperature Control\",\"detail\":\"Easy-to-adjust thermostat for precise heat settings on different fabric types.\"},{\"title\":\"Reliable and Long-Lasting\",\"detail\":\"Built with quality components to withstand regular daily use.\"}]', NULL),
(142, '300W Solar Generator', 'Solar Generator', 77, 166000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699c505772f825.38090441.png', '300W Solar Generator – Portable Power Wherever You Go\r\n\r\nThe 300W Solar Generator is a compact, reliable, and eco-friendly power solution designed to keep your essential devices running without reliance on the grid. Whether you’re camping, working outdoors, preparing for emergency power outages, or powering small appliances at home, this versatile solar generator delivers clean, silent energy with exceptional convenience.', '2026-02-23 13:04:23', 'uploads/image_1_699c5057733a85.85179700.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_699c5057734923.72914432.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '300w, solar, generator, portable', '[{\"title\":\"300W Output Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Provides dependable power for lights, small appliances, phones, laptops, fans, cameras, and more.\"},{\"title\":\"Portable & Lightweight\",\"detail\":\"Easy to carry with an ergonomic handle, perfect for travel, outdoor adventures, home use, and mobile workstations.\"},{\"title\":\"Multiple Ports & Outputs\",\"detail\":\"Equipped with AC outlet(s), USB ports, DC outputs, and other connection options to charge several devices at once.\"},{\"title\":\"Solar-Ready Charging\",\"detail\":\"Works seamlessly with solar panels (sold separately) for sustainable off-grid power generation.\"},{\"title\":\"Quiet and Clean Energy\",\"detail\":\"Unlike noisy fuel generators, this model operates silently with zero emissions \\u2014 ideal for indoor and outdoor environments.\"},{\"title\":\"Built-In Safety Protections\",\"detail\":\"Includes overcharge, short-circuit, and temperature protections to keep your electronics safe.\"}]', NULL),
(143, 'RFID Hotel Smart Lock', 'RFID Hotel Smart Lock', 90, 63000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699d95ad1169c5.80580990.jpeg', 'RFID Hotel Smart Locks\r\n\r\nUpgrade your hotel security and guest experience with our premium RFID Hotel Smart Locks — designed for modern hospitality environments that demand convenience, security, and durability.\r\n\r\nBuilt with high-grade stainless steel and advanced RFID technology, these smart locks allow guests to access their rooms effortlessly using key cards. No traditional keys. No security worries. Just seamless, secure entry.', '2026-02-24 12:12:29', 'uploads/image_1_699d95ad1180b7.63318934.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_699d95ad118e52.80331557.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', 'RFID, card access, smart lock, encrypted smart ', '[{\"title\":\"RFID Card Access System\",\"detail\":\"Fast, keyless entry\"},{\"title\":\"Encrypted Smart Card Technology\",\"detail\":\"Prevents unauthorized access\"},{\"title\":\"Stainless Steel Body & Handle\",\"detail\":\"Durable and modern look\"},{\"title\":\"Hidden Mechanical Key Override\",\"detail\":\"Backup during emergencies\"},{\"title\":\"Hotel Management System Compatibility\",\"detail\":\"Easy room control\"},{\"title\":\"Card Programming & Deactivation\",\"detail\":\"Simple guest turnover\"},{\"title\":\"Low Battery Warning Alert\",\"detail\":\"Avoids unexpected lockouts\"},{\"title\":\"Anti-theft Alarm Function\",\"detail\":\"Extra security layer\"},{\"title\":\"Battery Powered Operation\",\"detail\":\"No complex wiring\"},{\"title\":\"Fits Standard Hotel Doors\",\"detail\":\"Easy installation\"}]', NULL),
(144, 'Solar Pump and Charge Controller (Intergrity 2hp)', 'Intergrity 2hp', 92, 45000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699d9b2140bfe5.70005200.jpeg', 'Solar Pump and Charge Controller (Integrity 2HP)\r\nPowerful. Reliable. Built for performance.\r\n\r\nThe Integrity 2HP Solar Pump and Charge Controller is a high-efficiency solar water pumping solution designed to deliver consistent water supply using clean, renewable energy. Ideal for homes, farms, boreholes, irrigation systems, and remote locations, this system eliminates dependence on fuel or unstable grid electricity.\r\n\r\nEngineered with a durable stainless steel submersible pump and an intelligent DC charge controller, it ensures optimal performance, energy efficiency, and long service life.', '2026-02-24 12:35:45', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699d9b2140db94.98773300.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '100%, Solar, High water, durable, energy ', '[{\"title\":\"100% Solar Powered\",\"detail\":\"Runs directly on solar energy \\u2014 no fuel costs, no electricity bills.\"},{\"title\":\"High Water Output (2HP Performance)\",\"detail\":\"Delivers strong water pressure suitable for deep boreholes and large-scale water demand.\"},{\"title\":\"Intelligent Charge Controller\",\"detail\":\"Optimizes power input, protects against overload, low voltage, and dry running.\"},{\"title\":\"Durable Stainless Steel Pump Body\",\"detail\":\"Corrosion-resistant and built for long-term underground use.\"},{\"title\":\"Energy Efficient Operation\",\"detail\":\"Maximizes solar panel performance for consistent daily water supply.\"},{\"title\":\"Low Maintenance Design\",\"detail\":\"Minimal servicing required compared to fuel-powered pumps.\"}]', NULL),
(145, 'Solar Pump and Charge Controller  (My home 1hp)', 'Solar Pump and Charge Controller  (My home 1hp)', 93, 450000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699d9f83f13f02.44703903.jpeg', 'Solar Pump and Charge Controller (My Home 1HP)\r\n\r\nReliable water supply made simple and affordable.\r\n\r\nThe My Home 1HP Solar Pump and Charge Controller is a compact, energy-efficient solar water pumping solution designed specifically for residential use. Perfect for homes, small farms, and shallow to medium-depth boreholes, this system delivers consistent water pressure using clean solar energy — without relying on unstable grid power or expensive fuel.\r\n\r\nBuilt with a durable stainless steel submersible pump and a smart charge controller, it ensures long-lasting performance, energy protection, and smooth daily operation.', '2026-02-24 12:54:27', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699d9f83f156d4.62531421.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other ', 'Solar, charge controller, pump ', '[{\"title\":\"Runs on Solar Energy\",\"detail\":\"No fuel costs. No electricity bills. Just dependable sunshine-powered performance.\"},{\"title\":\"Ideal for Home Use (1HP Power)\",\"detail\":\"Perfect for domestic water supply, overhead tanks, and light irrigation.\"},{\"title\":\"Smart Charge Controller Included\",\"detail\":\"Protects against overload, voltage fluctuations, and dry running for longer pump life.\"},{\"title\":\"Corrosion-Resistant Stainless Steel Body\",\"detail\":\"Designed for durability inside boreholes and underground water systems.\"},{\"title\":\"Energy Efficient & Cost Saving\",\"detail\":\"Maximizes solar output while minimizing operating costs.\"}]', NULL),
(146, 'Phillips low power dry iron', 'Phillips low power dry iron', 94, 30000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699daebfb42e46.02726768.jpeg', 'Phillips Low Power Dry Iron\r\n\r\nEnjoy smooth, wrinkle-free clothes with less power consumption. The Phillips Low Power Dry Iron is designed for efficient performance, fast heating, and easy handling — making it perfect for homes, hostels, and areas with low or unstable electricity supply.', '2026-02-24 13:59:27', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699daebfb44617.71002624.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Phillips', 'Phillips, dry iron, low power', '[{\"title\":\"Fast Heating, Powerful Performance\",\"detail\":\"Despite its low power consumption, this iron heats up quickly and delivers consistent, even heat to remove stubborn wrinkles with ease.\"},{\"title\":\"Low Power Consumption\",\"detail\":\"Specially designed to consume less electricity\"},{\"title\":\"Non-Stick Soleplate\",\"detail\":\"The smooth non-stick soleplate glides effortlessly over all fabric types, preventing sticking and protecting your clothes from burns.\"},{\"title\":\"Adjustable Temperature Control\",\"detail\":\"Easily adjust the heat settings to suit different fabrics \\u2014 cotton, silk, wool, polyester, and more.\"},{\"title\":\"Lightweight & Easy to Handle\",\"detail\":\"Ergonomic design with a comfortable grip makes ironing less stressful and more convenient.\"},{\"title\":\"Built for Durability\",\"detail\":\"Made with high-quality materials to ensure long-lasting performance and reliability.\"}]', NULL),
(147, '9 way enclosure box', '9 way enclosure box', 97, 8500.00, 'uploads/image_main_699ee722a4ab63.02279873.jpeg', '9 Way Enclosure Box\r\n\r\nKeep your electrical installations organized, protected, and professionally finished with the 9 Way Enclosure Box. Designed for safety and durability, this distribution box securely houses up to nine circuit breakers, making it ideal for residential and light commercial electrical systems.', '2026-02-25 12:12:18', 'uploads/image_1_699ee722a4c0c0.97859939.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_699ee722a4cb91.17029084.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '9way, enclosure box, 9-way capacity ', '[{\"title\":\"Maximum Protection\",\"detail\":\"This enclosure protects your circuit breakers from dust, accidental contact, and external damage.\"},{\"title\":\"9-Way Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Accommodates up to 9 MCBs (Miniature Circuit Breakers), allowing efficient power distribution and easy circuit management.\"},{\"title\":\"Transparent Protective Cover\",\"detail\":\"Features a durable, tinted transparent door that allows you to view breaker positions without opening the box, while still maintaining safety.\"},{\"title\":\"Easy Installation\",\"detail\":\"Designed for surface mounting with pre-marked knockouts for smooth cable entry and quick installation.\"}]', NULL),
(148, '6 Way Enclosure Box', '6 Way Enclosure Box', 98, 4500.00, 'uploads/image_main_699eeb6213c765.89270899.jpeg', '6 Way Enclosure Box\r\n\r\nKeep your electrical installations organized, protected, and professionally finished with the 6 Way Enclosure Box. Designed for safety and durability, this distribution box securely houses up to nine circuit breakers, making it ideal for residential and light commercial electrical systems.', '2026-02-25 12:30:26', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Other', '6-way, capacity, enclosure box', '[{\"title\":\"6-Way Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Accommodates up to 6 MCBs (Miniature Circuit Breakers), allowing efficient power distribution and easy circuit management.\"},{\"title\":\"Transparent Protective Cover\",\"detail\":\"Features a durable, tinted transparent door that allows you to view breaker positions without opening the box, while still maintaining safety.\"},{\"title\":\"Easy Installation\",\"detail\":\"Designed for surface mounting with pre-marked knockouts for smooth cable entry and quick installation.\"},{\"title\":\"Maximum Protection\",\"detail\":\"Built with high-quality, flame-retardant ABS material, this enclosure protects your circuit breakers from dust, accidental contact, and external damage.\"}]', NULL),
(149, '2 pole 63A DC Breakers', 'DC Breaker 2', 107, 8000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699ef0a3527da0.99908446.jpeg', '2 Pole 63A DC Breakers\r\n\r\nProtect your solar and DC power systems with the reliable and high-performance 2 Pole 63A DC Breaker. Designed for efficient circuit protection, this breaker ensures safe disconnection and overload protection in DC applications such as solar installations, battery systems, and inverters.\r\nBuilt for durability and precision, it automatically cuts off power during overloads or short circuits — preventing equipment damage and reducing fire risks.', '2026-02-28 14:28:28', 'uploads/image_1_699ef0a3529d06.12424880.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_699ef0a352ed26.05314668.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '2 pole, 63 Amp, DC, breakers ', '[{\"title\":\"63 Amp Current Rating\",\"detail\":\"Ideal for medium to high DC loads\"},{\"title\":\"2 Pole Protection\",\"detail\":\"Disconnects both positive and negative lines for maximum safety\"},{\"title\":\"High Breaking Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Fast response during overload or short circuit\"},{\"title\":\"Durable Flame-Retardant Housing\",\"detail\":\"Built to withstand heat and harsh conditions\"},{\"title\":\"Clear ON\\/OFF Indicator\",\"detail\":\"Easy status visibility\"},{\"title\":\"DIN Rail Mount Design\",\"detail\":\"Quick and secure installation\"}]', NULL),
(150, '1 pole 63A DC Breaker', 'DC Breaker 2', 107, 6000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699ef45b31a5c4.19161326.jpeg', '1 Pole 63A DC Breaker\r\n\r\nEnsure reliable protection for your solar and DC electrical systems with the 1 Pole 63A DC Breaker. Designed specifically for direct current (DC) applications, this breaker provides fast and efficient protection against overloads and short circuits — helping to safeguard your valuable equipment.\r\n\r\nWith a 63 Amp current rating, it is ideal for medium to high-capacity DC installations, especially in solar power systems, battery banks, and inverter setups.', '2026-02-28 14:55:41', 'uploads/image_1_699ef45b31bbb3.09040738.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_699ef45b321589.72717680.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'SeanRo', '1 pole, 63A, DC , breaker ', '[{\"title\":\"63A Current Rating\",\"detail\":\"Suitable for high DC loads\"},{\"title\":\"Single Pole Protection\",\"detail\":\"Designed to protect one live conductor\"},{\"title\":\"High Breaking Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Quickly interrupts fault currents\"},{\"title\":\"DC Rated Performance\",\"detail\":\"Built specifically for solar and DC systems\"},{\"title\":\"Flame-Retardant Casing\",\"detail\":\"Durable and heat-resistant material\"},{\"title\":\"Clear ON\\/OFF Indicator\",\"detail\":\"Easy operational visibility\"},{\"title\":\"DIN Rail Mounting\",\"detail\":\"Fast and secure installation\"}]', NULL),
(152, '1 Pole 63A AC Breaker', 'AC Breaker 1', 106, 6000.00, 'uploads/image_main_699ef940a3b937.36720579.jpeg', '1 Pole 63A AC Breaker – Reliable Protection for Your Electrical System\r\n\r\nThe 1 Pole 63A AC Breaker is a high-performance miniature circuit breaker designed to safeguard your electrical circuits from overloads and short circuits. Engineered for durability, efficiency, and safety, this breaker is ideal for residential, commercial, and industrial installations where dependable AC protection is required.', '2026-02-28 14:27:27', NULL, 'uploads/image_2_699ef940a3ce07.02905029.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Other', '1 pole, 63amps , breaker, AC', '[{\"title\":\"1 Pole Design\",\"detail\":\"Provides single-phase protection for circuits, ensuring efficient control of individual lines.\"},{\"title\":\"63 Amp Capacity\",\"detail\":\"Robust current rating suitable for medium-duty loads such as lighting circuits, appliances, motors, and general power distribution.\"},{\"title\":\"Fast Tripping Response\",\"detail\":\"Quickly interrupts electrical flow during overloads or short circuits to protect wiring and connected equipment.\"},{\"title\":\"Standard AC Rating\",\"detail\":\"Designed for alternating current systems in homes, offices, and industrial environments.\"},{\"title\":\"IEC Standard Compliance\",\"detail\":\"Manufactured to meet international safety and performance standards, ensuring long-lasting reliability.\"},{\"title\":\"Easy Installation\",\"detail\":\"Compact and user-friendly design allows for quick mounting on DIN rails in electrical panels.\"}]', NULL),
(153, '2 Pole 63A AC Breaker', 'AC Breaker 1', 106, 6000.00, 'uploads/image_main_69a301caaac718.10715383.jfif', '2 Pole 63A AC Breaker\r\n\r\nProtect your electrical system with the 2 Pole 63A AC Breaker, a reliable circuit protection device designed to safeguard residential, commercial, and industrial electrical installations from overloads and short circuits.\r\n\r\nThis breaker disconnects both live and neutral lines simultaneously, ensuring enhanced safety and full isolation of the electrical circuit. With a 63 Amp current rating, it is ideal for heavy electrical loads such as air conditioners, water heaters, distribution boards, and inverter systems.\r\n\r\nBuilt with durable, flame-retardant materials and precision engineering, the 2 Pole 63A AC Breaker delivers dependable performance and long-term reliability for modern electrical systems.', '2026-02-28 14:55:06', 'uploads/image_1_69a301caaae1a8.62783212.jfif', 'uploads/image_2_69a301caaaf5a7.74978540.jfif', NULL, 0, 'Other', 'AC, 2pole, Breakers', '[{\"title\":\"63A Current Rating \",\"detail\":\" Handles high electrical loads efficiently\"},{\"title\":\"2-Pole Protection \",\"detail\":\"Disconnects both live and neutral for maximum safety\"},{\"title\":\"Overload & Short-Circuit Protection \",\"detail\":\"Prevents damage to electrical equipment\"},{\"title\":\"High Breaking Capacity \",\"detail\":\"Quickly interrupts fault currents\"},{\"title\":\"Durable Flame-Retardant Housing \",\"detail\":\"Designed for long-lasting use\"},{\"title\":\"Clear ON\\/OFF Indicator \",\"detail\":\"Easy to monitor circuit status\"},{\"title\":\"DIN Rail Mount Design \",\"detail\":\" Quick and secure installation in distribution boards\"}]', NULL),
(154, 'PABX Switch 16 Extension', 'Telephone Switching System', 125, 95000.00, 'uploads/image_main_69a81ac1c03283.90210377.jpeg', 'PABX Switch 16 Extension\r\n\r\nThe PABX Switch 16 Extension is a reliable telephone switching system designed to streamline communication within offices, hotels, schools, and business environments. It allows multiple internal telephone extensions to connect through a single central system, enabling seamless internal communication and efficient call management.\r\n\r\nWith support for up to 16 extensions, this PABX system reduces communication costs by allowing internal calls between staff without using external phone lines. It also enhances productivity by offering useful call management features such as call transfer, call forwarding, and caller ID support.', '2026-03-04 11:47:27', 'uploads/image_1_69a81ac1c04b94.22894406.jpeg', 'uploads/image_2_69a81ac1c05566.38900679.jpeg', NULL, 0, 'Pabx', 'Pabx, 16 extension, intercom system, telephone, communication system ', '[{\"title\":\"Supports Up to 16 Extensions\",\"detail\":\"Connect multiple office telephones to one central communication system.\"},{\"title\":\"Internal Call Communication\",\"detail\":\"Staff can call each other internally without using external phone networks.\"},{\"title\":\"Caller ID Support\",\"detail\":\"Displays incoming caller information for better call management.\"},{\"title\":\"Call Forwarding\",\"detail\":\"Forward calls to another extension when unavailable.\"},{\"title\":\"Call Transfer Function\",\"detail\":\"Transfer incoming calls to another office or department easily.\"},{\"title\":\"Three-Way Conferencing\",\"detail\":\"Allows multiple participants to join a single conversation.\"},{\"title\":\"Compact & Durable Design\",\"detail\":\"Designed for long-term operation with stable performance.\"}]', NULL);

